{"tid":565152,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"召集所有修讀CS的臉孔！","createTime":"2018-02-18T17:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T03:18:24.000Z","uid":172322,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"41ccb8adff93e287a952ff410557fa70940cc3d6","tid":565152,"uid":172322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:02:01.000Z","msg":"召喚所有正在修讀計算機科學的香港學生，不論是本地學生或是留學生都歡迎加入！<br />\n<br />\n在下希望能夠建立專屬於現任CS大學生的交流平台，以供交流實習、工作或是學習的資訊。在這裡你有機會能找到未來創業的小伙伴，可以任意諮詢的導師，和你一樣被編程所折磨的朋友，以及像你一樣熱愛著CS和編程的同好！希望藉著建立學生網絡，可以互相幫助對方度過艱辛的大學生涯，歡迎提出任何學術上的問題，進行各方面的學術性討論，在龐大的網絡中一定能遇到能解答你困憂的人；也無限歡迎想分享知識或是想法的人！一起建立一個長久的學生網絡吧！<br />\n<strong><br />\n有興趣既朋友請填FORM～<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/M50CpPsV0D2nlqCj1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FM50CpPsV0D2nlqCj1&d=2bcU3BXsMNDy0vb8v51sIDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=7eb3a62a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/M50CpPsV0D2nlqCj1</a></strong>"},{"pid":"d8d38b2d3daa5a7a632fea99861d4daaff4777af","tid":565152,"uid":172322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T03:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推post<br />\n在下目前係英國讀cs yr1<br />\n有少少好奇同香港課程係會差幾遠<br />\n而家programming主要係學java <br />\n目前學到awt同swing果d framework<br />\n學緊UML同unix bash<br />\n同埋順便想知道係咪無咩香港人會山長水遠黎英國讀cs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無其他讀cs既巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326e8ebbafb2696d373e36b4a181f99d6c7651d0","tid":565152,"uid":126510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"why dont you just leave your tg here"},{"pid":"8e64029922d27e50aab373932f50734936c97462","tid":565152,"uid":96741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"326e8ebbafb2696d373e36b4a181f99d6c7651d0","tid":565152,"uid":126510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"why d